****************
REMITTANCE FLOWS
****************
Author: Roxana Torre - www.torre.nl

A visualization of remittance flows based on d3.js chord layout. 
Note that the original d3.js file has been modified to fit the requirements.

The visualization can be found at www.torre.nl/remittances.

Data
"Bilateral remittance estimates using migrant stocks, destination country incomes, and source country incomes" (World Bank) which can be downloaded here: http://go.worldbank.org/JITC7NYTT0


